precis:
Amendment to SCHEDULE I to the PUBLIC SERVICE STAFF RELATIONS ACT which
adds the NATIONAL ENERGY BOARD to the list of those portions of the public
service of Canada that are separate employers, effective Dec. 31, 1992.
